{"type": "article", "id": 34233, "title": "无印良品的高端线Labo要换设计师，你知道这个系列吗？", "description": "Labo一般只在大型店铺出售，它的风格过往有很浓重的工装痕迹。", "date": "2016-11-08T23:34:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 303, "name": "无印良品"}, {"id": 707, "name": "Margaret Howell"}, {"id": 34701, "name": "MUJI Labo"}, {"id": 34727, "name": "Obana Daisuke"}, {"id": 34728, "name": "TARO HORIUCHI"}], "category": 19, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 99, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161108233151vs92Cc1ZzxAEqBKm.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">无印良品旗下那个价格更高的 MUJI Labo 要换时装设计师了。</p><p class=\"\">5 年前，这个价格比较偏高的系列由英国设计师 Margaret Howell 参与设立。此次人员变动后，Labo 系列的男装设计将由 N.Hoolywood 的尾花大辅（Obana Daisuke）主持，而女装则由拥有 TARO HORIUCHI 品牌的堀内太郎来负责。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109074620BRePlYgcMW9T0HAD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">尾花大辅设计作品，图片来源：<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" jsaction=\"mousedown:irc.rl;keydown:irc.rlk\" data-noload=\"\" tabindex=\"0\" href=\"http://www.essential-homme.com/n-hoolywood-new-york-menswear-springsummer-2015/\" data-ved=\"0ahUKEwiYvfCSqprQAhXEv1QKHVqIBjsQjB0IBg\">Essential Homme</a></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611090747092OcMUvXlBdWGLVfJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">尾花大辅设计作品，图片来源：<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" jsaction=\"mousedown:irc.rl;keydown:irc.rlk\" data-noload=\"\" tabindex=\"0\" href=\"http://www.essential-homme.com/n-hoolywood-new-york-menswear-springsummer-2015/\" data-ved=\"0ahUKEwjmqNOXqprQAhXKxlQKHZY2BREQjB0IBg\">Essential Homme</a></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109074845c7MaEuGAvDnlQ293.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.666292\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">堀内太郎设计女装，图片来源：<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" jsaction=\"mousedown:irc.rl;keydown:irc.rlk\" data-noload=\"\" tabindex=\"0\" href=\"http://www.thecoolhour.com/2014/11/taro-horiuchi-winter-2014-collection/\" data-ved=\"0ahUKEwiSnL-Tq5rQAhXpgFQKHdJoDOAQjB0IBg\">The Cool Hour&nbsp;</a></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109074956drDX1xPihjZavA4F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">堀内太郎设计女装，图片来源：<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" jsaction=\"mousedown:irc.rl;keydown:irc.rlk\" data-noload=\"\" tabindex=\"0\" href=\"http://www.lutelier.com/lute/details/index/161\" data-ved=\"0ahUKEwjX8unzqprQAhVix1QKHTlEBfwQjB0IBg\">Lutelier</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">和无印良品的其他产品一样，它的衣服裤子看起来也相当基本款。它们并不标榜形式上的设计，而更注重质地。如果你走进无印良品的商店，可能唯一能注意到也只是这些衣服的颜色：藏青色、卡其色、黑色、白色，反而会忽略衣服本身长什么样。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161108233202VySj9zlY80QmxZPo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611082332555GLerxDujIfia8UM.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663946\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">2002 年，无印良品曾和山本耀司合作制造服装，其中一款著名设计是水洗棉衬衣。不过这款衬衣看起来也并不太山本耀司，完全是无印良品的风格。</p><p class=\"\">”我们通过协商，明确了两家公司的分工。耀司公司以往的产品所显示出来的设计，大胆的剪裁及用色，都无法直接运用在无印良品服装上。不管怎么样，衣服的设计，用色都必须符合无印良品的设计，在此基础上与禁欲主义结合，而这就是我们拜托耀司公司设计的基本要求。”时任良品计划株式会社销售部长加藤隆志在《无印良品的改革》一书中这样回忆了和山本耀司的合作。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109071715X14Evb6mjwOgiyFV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.399457\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Hope Eli Blouse，图片来源：<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" jsaction=\"mousedown:irc.rl;keydown:irc.rlk\" data-noload=\"\" tabindex=\"0\" href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/tribaltrend/yohji-yamamoto/\" data-ved=\"0ahUKEwjU773UoJrQAhXCgrwKHdONCboQjB0IBg\">Pinterest</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">可以看出，尽管无印良品找来了风格突出的设计师合作，但服装风格依然很自我。这 5 年来的 MUJI Labo 的“境遇”稍微好一点，因为它至少还有那么点 &nbsp;Margaret Howell 的“真情流露”。</p><p class=\"\">英国服装设计师 Margaret Howell 主导设计的&nbsp;MUJI Labo 是 Laboratory （实验室）的简称，设计比较细致，比如上衣会专门设计放笔的小口袋。在店内，这个系列也和其他成衣分开陈列。如果你熟悉 Mergaret Howell，你会在 Labo 系列里找到很多相似的设计，只不过材质稍次，价格更低。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109072627m1WIFXaUGM367S8z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.687285\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>MUJI Labo，图片来源：<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" jsaction=\"mousedown:irc.rl;keydown:irc.rlk\" data-noload=\"\" tabindex=\"0\" href=\"http://www.muji.net/store/pc/user/clothes/labo/index.html\" data-ved=\"0ahUKEwju_7rFpZrQAhVBwrwKHdCUBn8QjB0IBg\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">無印良品</a></p></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109072738PRwd1ftqLojaMsyu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.687285\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>MUJI Labo，图片来源：<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" jsaction=\"mousedown:irc.rl;keydown:irc.rlk\" data-noload=\"\" tabindex=\"0\" href=\"http://www.muji.net/store/pc/user/clothes/labo/index.html\" data-ved=\"0ahUKEwiy_IDvpZrQAhVK7mMKHd6NCt0QjB0IBg\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">無印良品</a></p></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109072843ZesEpcABTROFb90w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.412371\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">上衣口袋细节，图片来源：<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" jsaction=\"mousedown:irc.rl;keydown:irc.rlk\" data-noload=\"\" tabindex=\"0\" href=\"http://www.muji.net/store/pc/user/clothes/labo/index.html\" data-ved=\"0ahUKEwiXsd2xpprQAhUL7GMKHQroCWIQjB0IBg\">無印良品</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">1946 年出生的 Margaret Howell 被誉为“英国国宝级设计师”，同时擅长男女装的设计。在 1970 年，她就曾为&nbsp;Elizabeth Taylor 设计过戏服。她的同名品牌的设计有几分书卷气、省时、中性，同样讲究穿着舒适，偏爱自然色调，也提倡低调气质。而 MUJI Labo 并没有太委屈 Margaret Howell 的灵感，还算是继续发挥了她同名品牌的精髓。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109073142EFwLn1HbUp7of5y0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679265\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Margaret Howell 设计品牌，图片来源：<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" jsaction=\"mousedown:irc.rl;keydown:irc.rlk\" data-noload=\"\" tabindex=\"0\" href=\"https://womanswork.co/2014/01/22/margaret-howell/\" data-ved=\"0ahUKEwjAnO2Np5rQAhUT8mMKHURCBkkQjB0IBg\">woman's work</a></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109073259H9Mcl2yU7XmribdR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.366667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" jsaction=\"mousedown:irc.rl;keydown:irc.rlk\" data-noload=\"\" tabindex=\"0\" href=\"http://www.fashionreview.co.uk/margaret-howell-fashion/\" data-ved=\"0ahUKEwj85r-zp5rQAhUJKGMKHXArAeoQjB0IBg\">London Fashion Review</a></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109073357oXVphtR21OvTNsAE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.928333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Margaret Howell 设计品牌男装，图片来源：<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" jsaction=\"mousedown:irc.rl;keydown:irc.rlk\" data-noload=\"\" tabindex=\"0\" href=\"http://www.fashionreview.co.uk/margaret-howell-fashion/\" data-ved=\"0ahUKEwiUgq_Np5rQAhVJ3WMKHYbfBBoQjB0IBg\">London Fashion Review</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">总的来说，和加藤隆志想要保持的“符合的无印良品的设计”的初衷一致，MUJI 请来的时装设计师不会太张扬自己的风采。尾花大辅的设计风格是街头，具体会怎么表现，也值得期待。</p><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图和文内图来自：<a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/fashion-news/muji-labo-designer-2017/#\" rel=\"nofollow\">popbee.com</a>。</p>"}